description: Elon Musk praises Nvidia CEO Jensen Huang's work ethics and attitude in an old video shared by Bloomberg. Huang mentions his early work experience at Denny's. Musk appreciates Huang's approach during Covid, ensuring necessities in Tesla factories, and acknowledges Ashok Elluswamy's role in Tesla's Autopilot team.
title: Nvidia CEO says he has cleaned 'lots of' toilets: Musk responds

description: Former executives of Outcome Health sentenced for their roles in a billion-dollar fraud scheme. Deceived clients, lenders, and investors by overbilling and inflating metrics. Justice served with prison and halfway house sentences. Company's reputation tarnished.
title: Indian-American CEO of tech startup charged in billion dollar fraud
